    AbstractDynamicBatchProcessor
    A batch processor that dynamically distributes queries to worker threads.
    AbstractDynamicBatchProcessorBuilder
    Builder class for a AbstractDynamicBatchProcessor.

    A batch processor that statically distributes a set of queries among several threads.
    AbstractStaticBatchProcessorBuilder
    A builder for a AbstractStaticBatchProcessor.
    BatchProcessor
    A markup interface for classes that can process a batch of work in a parallel environment (e.g. a MembershipOracle when used by a ParallelOracle).
    DynamicParallelOmegaOracle
    A specialized AbstractDynamicBatchProcessor for OmegaMembershipOracles that implements ParallelOmegaOracle.
    DynamicParallelOmegaOracleBuilder
    A specialized AbstractDynamicBatchProcessorBuilder for OmegaMembershipOracles.
    DynamicParallelOracle
    A specialized AbstractDynamicBatchProcessor for MembershipOracles that implements ParallelOracle.
    DynamicParallelOracleBuilder
    A specialized AbstractDynamicBatchProcessorBuilder for MembershipOracles.
    ParallelOmegaOracle
    ParallelOracle equivalent for OmegaMembershipOracle.
    ParallelOracle
    Basic interface for MembershipOracles that can process queries in parallel.
    StaticParallelOmegaOracle
    A specialized AbstractStaticBatchProcessor for OmegaMembershipOracles that implements ParallelOmegaOracle.
    StaticParallelOmegaOracleBuilder
    A specialized AbstractStaticBatchProcessorBuilder for OmegaMembershipOracles.
    StaticParallelOracle
    A specialized AbstractStaticBatchProcessor for MembershipOracles that implements ParallelOracle.
    StaticParallelOracleBuilder
    A specialized AbstractStaticBatchProcessorBuilder for MembershipOracles.
    ThreadPool
    A markup interface for a component that manages a pool of threads that may want to be shut down after usage.
    ThreadPool.PoolPolicy
    The policy for dealing with thread pools.
